# Data science & analysis

- Prefer `renv` (or documented env); `set.seed` when randomness matters.
- Document data lineage (`data/raw` vs `data/processed`); SPSS/Stata via **haven** when applicable.
- Do not invent GUI steps for SmartPLS / EViews — document exports and dictionaries.
- Use `data-analyst-r` persona for pipeline design; keep reports runnable headless where possible.
